Package: PSweight.sga
Type: Package
Title: PSweight.sga: Propensity Score Weighting for Causal Subgroup Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2022-03-21
Authors@R: c(person("Siyun","Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
